snippet.title: KIPP: Redux | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Karmen's Interactive PlayPlace!

After years of ups and downs, SafeFelt Toys has rebranded and opened a pizza parlor! Get through the 5 nights and collect your paycheck, hopefully you'll be in one piece.

This is a remaster of the game that I originally posted on TGC Games, This version comes with improved sounds, graphics, and it runs faster.

GameJolt Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/KIPPRedux/664831
Itch Link: https://jupitr-entertainment.itch.io/kipp-redux
